{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_016", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡在拍卖会上看到一块破旧的铜牌，没人出价。他花了十两银子买了下来。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡在突破元婴期时遭遇天劫，铜牌突然飞出，化作一面护盾挡住了九道天雷。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_017", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "师父递给陈凡一枚普通的玉佩，说是他入门时留下的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡将灵力注入玉佩，其中浮现出一段影像——是他从未谋面的父母留下的遗言。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_018", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "宗门后山的古井每到月圆之夜会发出幽幽的蓝光，长老说那是禁地。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡在调查魔教阴谋时跳入古井逃生，发现井底连接着一处上古传送阵。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_019", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "藏经阁三楼有一本无人能打开的石书，上面刻着古老的符文。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡用精血滴在石书上，书页翻开，记载着一门早已失传的炼体功法。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_020", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡在梦中反复看到一座黑色的塔，塔顶站着一个黑衣人。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "魔教总坛就是那座黑塔。黑衣人正是魔教教主，与陈凡有着宿命的纠葛。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_021", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王猛捡到了一片奇特的鳞片，坚硬无比，边缘有烧焦的痕迹。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡认出这是上古神龙的逆鳞，可以用来炼制一件防御法宝。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_022", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "宗门门口的老槐树下埋着一坛酒，据说只有掌门才能喝。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡继任掌门那天，挖出酒坛，坛底刻着一行小字——'遇魔教破阵时饮此酒'。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_023", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡的灵兽小火狐最近总是往北山跑，每次回来身上都沾着一种红色泥土。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "北山深处有一座赤焰矿脉，红色泥土是极品火灵石的风化物。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_024", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "山下李铁匠说他的锤子是祖传的，已经传了七代，从不离身。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "low"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "魔教攻山时李铁匠抡起锤子一锤砸碎了敌人的法宝——他竟是隐世多年的炼器宗师。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_025", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡在一次任务中救了一个昏迷的魔教弟子，发现他怀中有一块双鱼玉佩。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "玉佩的另一半在掌门手中，陈凡这才知道这个魔教弟子是掌门失散多年的儿子。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_026", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "长老殿中有一幅古画，画上的仙人手指指向天穹的某个方向。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡根据画中指引找到了天外陨石坠落之地，获得了一块星辰铁。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_027", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡练剑时总觉得自己的剑在微微颤抖，像是在共鸣什么。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "原来这柄剑中封印着一道剑灵，是上古剑仙的一缕残魂。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_028", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "每到下雨天，后山禁地就会传出若有若无的哭声。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "禁地下镇压着一个上古魔头的封印，哭声是封印松动的迹象。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_029", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡在秘境中带出了一颗不会发芽的种子，无论用什么方法都无法催活。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "这颗种子需要吸收天劫之力才能发芽。陈凡渡劫时种子吸收了雷霆之力，长成了世界树幼苗。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_030", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "师父每次喝醉都会念叨一句话：'我对不起一个人'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "当年师父为了守护宗门，不得不放弃了自己的道侣。那人正是魔教如今的右护法。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_031", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "藏经阁管理员每次看到陈凡都会多看他两眼，欲言又止。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "管理员其实是上任掌门易容假扮的，一直在暗中观察陈凡是否堪当大任。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_032", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "宗门的灵脉近年来逐渐枯竭，长老们找不到原因。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "灵脉的源头被一头沉睡的地龙堵住了。陈凡深入地下与地龙沟通，让它挪开了身体。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_033", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈凡在集市上买了一把生锈的短剑，卖剑的人说是在古战场上捡的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "low"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "短剑上的锈迹被灵力震落后，露出了'轩辕'二字——这是黄帝曾经的佩剑碎片。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_034", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "师妹苏晴最近总是走神，练功时心不在焉。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "她收到了一封匿名信，说她的亲生父母还活着，约她去城南破庙见面。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xianxia_035", "genre": "xianxia", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "天剑宗的镇派之宝——天剑——在剑冢中鸣动了三声。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "这是千年未有之事。掌门说这是天剑在择主，意味着新的剑主即将出现。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
